{"tid":2012014,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩香港電影你覺得值得被加入到Criterion Collection","createTime":"2020-05-11T11:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T03:59:40.000Z","uid":78390,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"61a8d4b94ac208d716001bdaf368582efc58b49b","tid":2012014,"uid":78390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T11:28:45.000Z","msg":"The Criterion Collection 係一個專門發行當代電影傑作嘅電影發行公司 佢地有最專業嘅復修技術 可以將舊電影修補重整到4K去保全傑作 所以被收錄嘅電影都係電影歷史視為重要而不可或缺 現今大都認為The Criterion Collection 係電影權威 永遠以推廣電影藝術為佢地中旨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qOVcRQF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqOVcRQF.jpg&h=9569658a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.criterion.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.criterion.com%2F&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HRmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=7f86bbca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.criterion.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n有不少香港電影都被收錄到The Criterion Collection <br />\n王家衛嘅作品更加係The Criterion Collection 嘅生招牌<br />\n花樣年華(Spine 147) 同重慶森林 (Spine 453)<br />\n係Criterion Channel有墮落天使同春光乍洩可惜冇出碟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cfwb7pG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcfwb7pG.jpg&h=0aaacd4b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AxL4HX2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAxL4HX2.jpg&h=472a3f63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吳宇森作品喋血雙雄（Spine 8) 同鎗神(Spine 9) 都記錄在內<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AEz1LbB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAEz1LbB.jpg&h=9398f632&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tuxyBih.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtuxyBih.png&h=b2938f1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成龍嘅警察故事(Spine 971) 同警察故事2 (Spine 972) <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SqCF0K2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSqCF0K2.png&h=9ef70acf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RQDU5bJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRQDU5bJ.jpg&h=3959968e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近李小龍都慶幸被The Criterion Collection 收錄 Bruce Lee: His Greatest Hit (Spine 1036) 內有齊佢係嘉禾嘅作品<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyHe5b5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyHe5b5.png&h=748a5630&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實香港電影咁勁應該都好要收錄 唔知大家會想咩電影收錄在The Criterion Collection <br />\n<br />\n西遊記第壹佰零壹回之月光寶盒同西遊記大結局之仙履奇緣呢兩部電影都好希望會收錄到The Criterion Collection <br />\n其實西游記呢個名著都經常返拍 而呢一部應該係最有特色 加上係周星馳當代最強最搞笑香港演員 呢部經典入到The Criterion Collection 一定讓外國人更加了解香港電影<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nNcrbSh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnNcrbSh.jpg&h=31d2b450&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DyQgy5D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyQgy5D.jpg&h=2dd6c85e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f62327365bb32a99286fa99187e3d94e61b5329","tid":2012014,"uid":162539,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T11:31:31.000Z","msg":"諗起東邪西毒個母帶損毁左。基本上修復唔返"},{"pid":"51e9d743c3fa39a1b3b825f951066ae76b08a432","tid":2012014,"uid":307329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T11:41:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c03022da02e913f7ba2b966d7db21e099f564f0d","tid":2012014,"uid":159266,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T11:47:18.000Z","msg":"一個字頭的誕生應該要復修"},{"pid":"9497247ffecf3357fc7e8e6cd991cc0579a72d2d","tid":2012014,"uid":42848,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T11:47:50.000Z","msg":"最後勝利<br />\n麥兜菠蘿油王子<br />\n一個字頭的誕生、暗花、鎗火 （唔一定criterion, 但值得修復）"},{"pid":"0c954de51063e2065761b93c0b27a2aca994314b","tid":2012014,"uid":103218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T11:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-55ca0ff59