":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T12:57:03.000Z","msg":"英雄本色重慶森林 不過鬼佬係鍾意成龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7262041a583ede5d92f8df616641071f9a286792","tid":2012014,"uid":192929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:40:58.000Z","msg":"乜代宗師<br />\n棟篤特工"},{"pid":"afbce9f4d0a94b8588adcd5310af88e92120a249","tid":2012014,"uid":48479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T13:42:02.000Z","msg":"董夫人<br />\n許鞍華越南三部曲boxset (來客、胡越的故事、投奔怒海)<br />\n劉家良&times;劉家輝boxset (少林三十六房、爛頭何、少林搭棚大師、武館、五郎八卦棍、霹靂十傑)"},{"pid":"60a32c43adb185451e53829ac3f8fe5c4a82586e","tid":2012014,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T18:50:11.000Z","msg":"父子情"},{"pid":"2e264450eef7223096bf572e63f9bafba56064d8","tid":2012014,"uid":40461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T03:59:40.000Z","msg":"Criterion好著重對電影嘅影響力，咁睇的話，最有機會加入嘅電影可能係無間道，徐克，殭屍系列"}]}